# Implementation Plan - Swap Monitor 1 and Monitor 2 Roles

The goal is to swap the roles of Monitor 1 and Monitor 2 in the application. Monitor 1 will become the "Extended Monitor" (external window output), and Monitor 2 will become the "Streaming/OBS" monitor (inline preview).

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This change will effectively swap the user's saved settings for Monitor 1 and Monitor 2 in the database. What was previously configured for "Streaming" (M1) will now apply to "Extended" (M1), and vice versa.

## Proposed Changes

